"请根据以下对话内容，为本次对话生成一个简短、精炼的标题。\n\n要求：\n- 长度在4到8个词之间。\n- 能准确概括对话的核心主题。\n- 直接返回标题内容，不要包含任何额外说明、引号或标点符号。\n\n对话内容：\n用户: %@\nAI: %@" = "Please generate a short, concise title for this conversation based on the content below.\n\nRequirements:\n- 4 to 8 words.\n- Accurately summarize the core topic of the conversation.\n- Return only the title text, without any extra notes, quotes, or punctuation.\n\nConversation:\nUser: %@\nAI: %@";
