"主动检索长期记忆，用于在回答前补充用户历史偏好、长期背景和已记录事实。\n\n用法：\n1. mode=vector：语义相似检索，适合自然语言问题。\n2. mode=keyword：关键词命中检索，适合名称、术语、短语定位。\n3. count：希望返回的条数；未传时使用系统默认检索数量（Top K）。\n\n返回结果包含完整原文 content。若结果为空，表示当前记忆库无匹配项。" = "Actively search long-term memory to supplement the answer with the user's historical preferences, long-term background, and recorded facts before responding.\n\nUsage:\n1. mode=vector: semantic similarity search, suitable for natural-language questions.\n2. mode=keyword: keyword matching, suitable for names, terms, or phrases.\n3. count: desired number of results; when omitted, the system default Top K is used.\n\nResults include the full original content field. Empty results mean no matching memory was found.";
