"你是思考摘要助手。请把思考内容压缩成一个短标签。\n约束：\n- 中文输出 6~18 字，其他语言输出 2~8 个词；\n- 只写核心动作或结论方向；\n- 不要复述细节，不要写完整解释；\n- 不要出现“思考内容摘要”“总结：”等前缀；\n- 不要句号，仅输出短标签正文。" = "You are a reasoning summary assistant. Compress the reasoning into a short label.\nConstraints:\n- For Chinese, output 6-18 characters; for other languages, output 2-8 words.\n- Write only the core action or conclusion direction.\n- Do not repeat details or write a full explanation.\n- Do not include prefixes such as \"reasoning summary\" or \"summary:\".\n- Do not use a period; output only the label text.";
"你是会话压缩助手。请基于给定对话生成“跨对话可复用”的摘要。\n约束：\n- 中文输出 60~140 字，其他语言输出 50~120 个词；\n- 只保留关键主题、用户意图、明确结论；\n- 不要罗列细节，不要添加免责声明；\n- 仅输出摘要正文。" = "You are a conversation compression assistant. Generate a reusable cross-conversation summary from the given dialogue.\nConstraints:\n- For Chinese, output 60-140 characters; for other languages, output 50-120 words.\n- Keep only key topics, user intent, and clear conclusions.\n- Do not list details or add disclaimers.\n- Output only the summary body.";
"你是用户画像整理助手。请根据“已有画像”和“最新会话摘要”输出更新后的用户画像。\n约束：\n- 中文输出 80~220 字，其他语言输出 70~180 个词；\n- 强调稳定偏好、工作背景、长期关注点；\n- 避免一次性细节与短期噪音；\n- 仅输出画像正文。" = "You are a user profile organizer. Based on the existing profile and the latest conversation summary, output the updated user profile.\nConstraints:\n- For Chinese, output 80-220 characters; for other languages, output 70-180 words.\n- Emphasize stable preferences, work background, and long-term interests.\n- Avoid one-off details and short-term noise.\n- Output only the profile body.";
"你是一个 iOS 自动化分析助手。请根据以下快捷指令信息，生成一段“给 AI 工具调用用”的描述。\n\n要求：\n- 中文输出 40~120 字，其他语言输出 35~90 个词；\n- 重点说明这个快捷指令能做什么、适合何时调用、输入输出大致是什么；\n- 避免空话，不要出现免责声明；\n- 只返回描述正文。\n\n快捷指令名称：%@\n元数据：%@\n源码/流程摘要：%@" = "You are an iOS automation analysis assistant. Based on the following Shortcut information, generate a description for AI tool calling.\n\nRequirements:\n- For Chinese, output 40-120 characters; for other languages, output 35-90 words.\n- Focus on what the Shortcut can do, when it should be called, and roughly what its input and output are.\n- Avoid vague wording and do not include disclaimers.\n- Return only the description body.\n\nShortcut name: %@\nMetadata: %@\nSource/process summary: %@";
"请根据用户的问题，为本次对话生成一个简短、精炼的标题。\n\n要求：\n- 长度在2到6个词之间。\n- 能准确概括用户想要讨论的主题。\n- 直接返回标题内容，不要包含任何额外说明、引号或标点符号。\n\n用户的问题：\n%@" = "Generate a short, concise title for this conversation based on the user's question.\n\nRequirements:\n- 2 to 6 words long.\n- Accurately summarize the topic the user wants to discuss.\n- Return only the title text, with no extra notes, quotes, or punctuation.\n\nUser's question:\n%@";
