"集中管理工具集成、语音能力与系统维护入口。" = "Manage tool integrations, voice features, and system maintenance entries in one place.";
"这个页面适合做什么\n• 统一进入进阶功能，不打断主聊天流程。\n• 快速定位语音、工具集成、导入和维护能力。\n\n入口建议\n• 工具中心：排查工具是否在当前会话可用。\n• 记忆系统 / 世界书：管理长期偏好与规则知识。\n• MCP / 快捷指令：接入外部能力和自动化流程。\n• 存储管理 / 远程文件访问：做维护与清理。\n\n使用建议\n• 先保证核心入口可用，再逐步开启实验功能。" = "What this page is for\n• Open advanced features without interrupting the main chat flow.\n• Quickly find voice, tool integration, import, and maintenance features.\n\nSuggested entries\n• Tool Center: check whether tools are available in the current session.\n• Memory / Worldbook: manage long-term preferences and rule knowledge.\n• MCP / Shortcuts: connect external capabilities and automation flows.\n• Storage Management / Remote File Access: maintain and clean up data.\n\nSuggestion\n• Keep core entries working first, then enable experimental features gradually.";
"统一管理语音输入与语音朗读。" = "Manage voice input and text-to-speech in one place.";
"配置 MCP 工具服务器，让助手调用外部能力。" = "Configure MCP tool servers so the assistant can call external capabilities.";
"导入快捷指令工具并控制 AI 的调用权限。" = "Import Shortcuts tools and control AI call permissions.";
"管理可按需加载的技能包，并控制是否向模型暴露 use_skill 工具。" = "Manage on-demand skill bundles and control whether the use_skill tool is exposed to the model.";
"管理世界书并绑定到当前会话。" = "Manage worldbooks and bind them to the current session.";
"查看并清理本地模型、文件与缓存。" = "Review and clean up local models, files, and caches.";
"支持导入 ETOS 数据包，也可通过第三方来源迁移。" = "Import ETOS data packages, or migrate from third-party sources.";
"让 AI 持续理解你的长期偏好和上下文。" = "Let AI keep understanding your long-term preferences and context.";
"能力说明\n• 记忆系统会在回复前检索历史信息，提升连续性。\n• 写入开关仅影响“新增记忆”，不影响读取已有记忆。\n\n推荐流程\n1. 先开启总开关体验效果。\n2. 对噪声敏感时可先关闭写入，仅保留读取。\n3. 定期到记忆库管理清理低质量记忆。" = "How it works\n• The memory system retrieves historical information before replies to improve continuity.\n• The write switch only affects new memories; existing memories can still be read.\n\nRecommended flow\n1. Turn on the main switch first and try the effect.\n2. If you are sensitive to noisy memories, disable writing and keep reading only.\n3. Clean up low-quality memories regularly in Memory Library.";
"启用后，AI 将拥有记忆系统能力。它会在每次对话前检索相关记忆，并能通过工具主动学习。" = "When enabled, AI gains memory capabilities. It retrieves relevant memories before each chat and can actively learn through tools.";
"关闭后仅读取记忆，不保存新内容。" = "When off, existing memories can still be read, but new content is not saved.";
"会话摘要存入会话 JSON，用户画像存入 Memory/user_profile.json。" = "Conversation summaries are saved in session JSON, and the user profile is saved in Memory/user_profile.json.";
"统一查看聊天可用工具，并集中调整启用状态。" = "Review chat-available tools and adjust enablement in one place.";
"页面作用\n• 快速判断各类工具在“配置层”与“会话层”是否真正可用。\n\n指标怎么读\n• 配置已启用：你在设置里已经打开。\n• 当前会话实际可用：在总开关、审批策略、隔离策略后仍可用。\n\n推荐流程\n1. 先看汇总数字，确认问题范围。\n2. 开启“仅显示已启用”缩小排查范围。\n3. 进入具体工具页调整策略与状态。\n\n常见情况\n• 如果显示世界书隔离生效，记忆、MCP、Agent Skills、快捷指令可能被会话策略屏蔽。" = "What this page does\n• Quickly check whether each tool category is truly available at the configuration and session layers.\n\nHow to read metrics\n• Configured enabled: enabled in Settings.\n• Available in current session: still available after the main switch, approval policy, and isolation policy.\n\nRecommended flow\n1. Check summary numbers first to narrow the issue.\n2. Enable Enabled Only to reduce the search scope.\n3. Open the specific tool page to adjust policy and status.\n\nCommon case\n• If Worldbook isolation is active, memory, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts may be blocked by session policy.";
"当前会话已启用世界书隔离发送，聊天时不会发送记忆、MCP、Agent Skills 与快捷指令工具。" = "Worldbook isolation is enabled for this session, so memory, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts tools will not be sent during chat.";
"统一查看已安装技能，并集中调整聊天暴露与单项启用状态。" = "Review installed skills and adjust chat exposure and per-skill enablement in one place.";
"总开关关闭后，下面的单项启用状态会保留，但聊天时不会实际暴露这些技能。" = "When the main switch is off, per-skill enablement is preserved but these skills are not exposed during chat.";
